[BID 1C] ⟦You open one\C with your long club suit.⟧ Partner responds one\H, showing four or more hearts.
[BID 2D] ⟦Over partner's one\H you reverse into two\D, showing extra strength and a second suit.⟧ Partner bids the fourth suit, two\S, Fourth Suit Forcing and game-going, asking you to keep describing.
